    "updated_at": "2014-01-08T16:31:38Z",
    "body": "Yeah, `#[unsafe_destructor]` seems like the right escape hatch.\n\nMaybe we should have two traits: `Drop` and `UnsafeDrop`, where the `drop` method on the latter is marked `unsafe`?\n",
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
