    "body": "I think UnsafeDrop would be the same as Drop, except that it avoids using an attribute and actually uses the `unsafe` keyword for easier greppability.\n\nI'm not sure that's unreasonable. Smart pointer destructors are nearly all unsafe anyway, as they deal with memory.\n",
